      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The Problem"
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "No proper support and customization services."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Problems encountered with the data migration process from one environment to another."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Issues with the customization of the production environment as the client wanted segregation of all entities (components, Dataverse Table, Multiple App in one solution, etc.) with their dependencies into a single solution."
        },
        {
          "t": "li",
          "text": "Difficulty in the creation of a new portal for the University’s alumni using the Power Platform (either Model-Driven App or Canvas app)."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Absence of support services"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Disruption in data migration process"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Disruption in production environment"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Difficulty to create a new portal"
        }
      ],
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The Problem"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Absence of support services"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Disruption in data migration process"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Disruption in production environment"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Difficulty to create a new portal"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [],
      "listItems": [
        "No proper support and customization services.",
        "Problems encountered with the data migration process from one environment to another.",
        "Issues with the customization of the production environment as the client wanted segregation of all entities (components, Dataverse Table, Multiple App in one solution, etc.) with their dependencies into a single solution.",
        "Difficulty in the creation of a new portal for the University’s alumni using the Power Platform (either Model-Driven App or Canvas app)."
      ],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 Solution"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 provides Power Apps solutions that are based on the MS Power Platform. Power Apps provides a rapid low code development environment for building custom apps for business needs. It has services, connectors, and a scalable data service and app platform (Microsoft Dataverse) to allow simple integration and interaction with existing data. Power Apps enables the creation of web and mobile applications that run on all devices."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "To resolve the issue regarding the production environment, we suggested following these steps for segregation."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Create a new solution."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Add its existing entities as per the app in this solution."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Add all their dependent objects."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Install dependency in production environment."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Publish all customization."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Export this solution."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Now Import this exported solution to the production."
        }
      ],
      "headings": [
        {
