        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 provides Power Apps solutions that are based on the MS Power Platform. Power Apps provides a rapid low code development environment for building custom apps for business needs. It has services, connectors, and a scalable data service and app platform (Microsoft Dataverse) to allow simple integration and interaction with existing data. Power Apps enables the creation of web and mobile applications that run on all devices."
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "To resolve the issue regarding the production environment, we suggested following these steps for segregation."
